<XCHELP topic=cmd_bell alias=bell>
<CENTER><FONT size=32 color=blue><B>/BELL</B></FONT></CENTER><BR><BR>
<PRE>
<B><U>Syntax:</U></B> /BELL

<B><U>Description:</U></B>
The /BELL commands rings the system BELL.
It may also cause some screen savers to terminate, and activate the display again, depends on the screen-saver program.

<B><U>History:</U></B>
The /BELL command first appeared in XChatter version 0.5beta2.
</PRE>
</XCHELP>
